Package: demoShiny
Title: Runs a Shiny app as demo or shows an overview of available Shiny apps
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
  person("Sigbert", "Klinke", email="sigbert@hu-berlin.de", role=c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Mimics the R `demo` functionality for Shiny apps in a package. In the subdirectory `inst/shiny` the apps should be stored and can be called by `demoShiny(topic)`.
Depends: shiny
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
